<div id="outline-container-org776eda4" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org776eda4"><span class="section-number-2">3</span> 使用org-mode编辑博客</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-3">
<p>
笔记导出：org-publish
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><a href="https://victor72.github.io/blog/2016/06/16/with-org-mode-setup-up-personal-blog/">使用 Emacs Org-Mode 写博客 - 日知录</a></li>
<li><a href="https://lgfang.github.io/computer/2015/11/02/org-mode-github-pages">用 Org-Mode 与 GithubPages 搭建个人博客</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga5e0c49" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga5e0c49"><span class="section-number-3">3.1</span> 导出配置</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-3-1">
<pre class="example">
(setq
      ;; nil as default to avoid leaking sensitive info unintentionally,
      ;; overwritten in per-project settings bellow
      org-html-postamble nil
      org-publish-project-alist
      '(
	("blog-attachments"
	 :base-directory "/mnt/c/myText/local-blog"
	 :base-extension "png\\|jpg"
	 :recursive t
	 :publishing-directory "/mnt/c/myText/blog/images"
	 :publishing-function org-publish-attachment)

	("blog"
	 :base-directory "/mnt/c/myText/local-blog"  
	 :base-extension "org"
	 :recursive t
	 :publishing-directory "/mnt/c/myText/blog/_posts"
	 :publishing-function org-html-publish-to-html
	 :body-only t ;; Only export section between &lt;body&gt; &lt;/body&gt;
	 :html-link-use-abs-url t
	 ))

      org-export-allow-bind-keywords t  ; I like "#+BIND:var value"
)
</pre>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org580dda0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org580dda0"><span class="section-number-4">3.1.1</span> 配置解读</h4>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0814fcd" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org0814fcd"><span class="section-number-3">3.2</span> 导出命令</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-3-2">
<p>
在emacs里=M-x org-publish RET blog RET=
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org975fde3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org975fde3"><span class="section-number-3">3.3</span> 注意事项</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-3-3">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>org文件命名格式：=yyyy:mm:dd-filename.org=</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
